name: MINGMING
description: $MING is inspired by Sachi, the cat that started it all — a reminder of simplicity, loyalty, and real Filipino vibes. We wanted to create a truly Filipino native token, something that feels ours. And what better name than “Ming Ming” — the most common and beloved name for pet cats across the Philippines. It’s familiar, it’s warm, and it instantly connects with every Filipino household. $MING isn’t just a meme — it’s culture, identity, and community rolled into one. From Sachi’s spirit to the Filipino heart, this token is built for the people, by the people.
